column3: You don't need to open a new pull, you could just force-push to your old branch and it would appear in your old issue (#3600).\n

Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/3078b582cc6c2e8389ef8e6b5807a51ebae7bf67 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
